00:14:11.487 --> 00:14:16.892
And then we hope that our armored,
professional personalities

00:14:16.916 --> 00:14:20.052
will prevent us from having our
heart broken in work.

00:14:20.685 --> 00:14:23.090
But if you're sincere about your work,

00:14:23.797 --> 00:14:25.407
it should break your heart.

00:14:25.993 --> 00:14:27.781
You should get to thresholds

00:14:27.805 --> 00:14:31.324
where you do not know how to proceed.

00:14:31.852 --> 00:14:35.208
You do not know how to get
from here to there.

00:14:36.619 --> 00:14:37.783
What does that do?

00:14:37.807 --> 00:14:41.059
It puts you into a proper
relationship with reality.

00:14:41.083 --> 00:14:42.233
Why?

00:14:42.257 --> 00:14:44.084
Because you have to ask for help.

00:14:50.779 --> 00:14:52.167
Heartbreak.

00:14:52.191 --> 00:14:54.303
